0and%20is%20near%20the%20sea%2C%20snow%20is%20relatively%20rare%20in%20Amsterdam.%20As%20such%2C%20when%20it%20does%20happen%2C%20it%20can%20have%20an%20outsize%20impact%20on%20travel.%20This%20week%2C%20several%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20snow%2C%20high%20winds%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20capacity%20for%20de-icing%20planes%20in%20the%20cold%20weather%2C%20have%20combined%20to%20exacerbate%20the%20disruption%20at%20Schiphol%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20Flightradar24%20showed%20the%20chaos%20on%20the%20tarmac%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20flight%20operated%20by%20KLM%2C%20the%20Dutch%20flag%20carrier%2C%20was%20supposed%20to%20take%20off%20for%20London%20at%209%20a.m.%20But%20after%20it%20left%20the%20gate%2C%20it%20taxied%20around%20the%20airport%20twice%20before%20going%20back%20to%20the%20gate%20after%20almost%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FP3khY%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bar%20chart%20showing%20the%20number%20of%20flights%20canceled%20at%20Amsterdam%20Schiphol%20Airport%20each%20day%20between%20Friday%2C%20January%202%2C%20and%20Tuesday%2C%20January%206%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FP3khY%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20ongoing%20winter%20weather%2C%20air%20traffic%20at%20Schiphol%20is%20disrupted%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20KLM%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20winter%20conditions%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight-tracking%20data%20also%20showed%20how%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-economy-class-emirates-a380-dubai-london-airport-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEmirates%20Airbus%20A380%3C%2Fa%3E%20spe