u%20says%20AI%20will%20need%2010%20'yottaflops'%20of%20compute%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20here's%20what%20that%20actually%20means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226727%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lisa%20su%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695cc1fc832e0ef1ead737d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224487%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAMD%20CEO%20Lisa%20Su%20says%20AI%20will%20soon%20need%20%26quot%3B10%20yottaflops%26quot%3B%20of%20compute%20%E2%80%94%20a%20scale%20of%20computing%20power%20the%20world%20has%20never%20built%20before.%3Cp%3ECaroline%20Brehman%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20will%20soon%20need%20%26quot%3B10%20yottaflops%26quot%3B%20of%20compute%2C%20said%20AMD%20CEO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHow%20many%20of%20you%20know%20what%20a%20yottaflop%20is%3F%26quot%3B%20Su%20asked%20the%20audience%20at%20CES%202026.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20never%2C%20ever%20been%20anything%20like%20this%20in%20the%20history%20of%20computing%2C%26quot%3B%20Su%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20needs%20so%20much%20computing%20power%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-lisa-su-ceo-and-president-of-advanced-micro-device%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMeet%2520Lisa%2520Su%253A%2520CEO%2520of%2COpenAI%2520With%2520Chips%2520%252D%2520Business%2520Insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAMD%20CEO%20Lisa%20Su%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20it%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20unit%20most%20people%20have%20never%20heard%20of%3A%20the%20yottaflop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESu%20said%20in%20her%20keynote%20at%20CES%202026%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20world%20would%20need%20more%20than%20%26quot%3B10%20yottaflops%26quot%3B%20of%20compute%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20measure%20of%20how%20fast%20a%20computer%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20AI's%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20many%20of%20you%20know%20what%20a%20yottaflop%20is%3F%26quot%3B%20Su%20asked%20the%20audience.%20%26quot%3BRaise%20your%20hand%2C%20please%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20before%20quickly%20explaining%20the%20term%20herself%20when%20no%20one%20appeared%20to%20raise%20their%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20yottaflop%20is%20a%20one%20followed%20by%2024%20zeros.%20So%2010%20yottaflop%20flops%20is%2010%2C000%20times%20more%20compute%20than%20we%20had%20in%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20computing%2C%20a%20flop%20is%20a%20single%20basic%20math%20calculation.%20A%20computer%20doing%201%20billion%20calculations%20per%20second%20is%20equal%20to%20a%20gigaflop.%20A%20yottaflop%20is%20equivalent%20to%20a%20computer%20performing%20one%20septillion%20calculations%20per%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20scientists%20say%2010%20yottaflops%20would%20be%20enough%20computing%20power%20to%20run%20complex%2C%20atom-level%20simulations%20for%20entire%20planets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20global%20AI%20compute%20stood%20at%20about%20one%20zettaflop%20%E2%80%94%20a%20one%20followed%20by%2021%20zeros.%20By%202025%2C%20Su%20said%2C%20that%20figure%20had%20already%20surged%20to%20more%20than%20100%20zettaflops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20never%2C%20ever%20been%20anything%20like%20this%20in%20the%20history%20of%20computing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESu's%2010%20yottaflop%20prediction%20is%20about%205.6%20million%20times%20faster%20than%20the%20most%20powerful%20supercomputer%20today%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Energy's%20El%20Capitan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20powering%20today's%20AI%20compute%20is%20already%20putting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-centers-us-chips-electricity-power-crunch-shortage-goldman-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrain%20on%20the%20US%20power%20grid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20