t%3BWe%20probably%20only%20did%20a%20couple%20more%20deals%20than%20in%202024%2C%20but%20our%20deal%20size%20almost%20doubled%2C%26quot%3B%20Gorius%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20about%2052%20deals%20last%20year%20and%20grossed%20around%20%24500%2C000.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20did%2054%20deals%20and%20grossed%20just%20over%20a%20million.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202026%2C%20the%20business%20partners%2C%20who%20primarily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investors-factors-to-consider-when-choosing-market-city-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvest%20in%20Louisville%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20say%20they%20are%20moving%20away%20from%20the%20strategy%20that%20helped%20them%20get%20their%20start%20in%20real%20estate%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-flipping-mistakes-avoid-common-costly-real-estate-tips-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflipping%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202026%2C%20we%20expect%20to%20do%20fewer%20flips%2C%26quot%3B%20Gorius%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnless%20it's%20an%20absolute%20home%20run%2C%20it%20just%20doesn't%20make%20as%20much%20sense%20in%20this%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6f09fb4-5e53-49c6-9eea-310bf5ff6188%5C%22%3EA%20slower%20market%20makes%20flipping%20riskier%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHart%20and%20Gorius%20said%20that%20their%20market%20has%20cooled%20significantly%2C%20making%20quick%20flip%20exits%20harder%20to%20count%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20around%20September%2C%20the%20market%20has%20dropped%20pretty%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20Hart%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Louisville%2C%20we've%20gone%20from%20about%202%2C500%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20to%20nearly%203%2C900.%20Days%20on%20market%20have%20tripled%20%E2%80%94%20now%20it's%20over%20a%20month%2C%20sometimes%20even%20two.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slowdown%20makes%20it%20even%20more%20imperative%20that%20they%20land%20a%20good%20deal%20on%20the%20front%20end%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20overpay%20for%20a%20property%2C%20you're%20not%20getting%20like%2010%20offers%20in%20the%20first%2024%20hours.%20It%20may%20sit%20on%20market%20for%20a%20month%20because%20you%20overpriced%20it%2C%20and%20then%20the%20price%20just%20continues%20to%20drop.%20So%20you%20really%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20buying%20at%20the%20right%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209d6e0c5-f710-4af3-a278-efe2ab1166c8%5C%22%3ELeaning%20into%20the%20BRRRR%20method%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20relying%20on%20flips%2C%20Gorius%20and%20Hart%20plan%20to%20lean%20more%20heavily%20into%20BRRRR%20projects%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShort%20for%20buy%2C%20rehab%2C%20rent%2C%20refinance%2C%20repeat%2C%20the%20BRRRR%20strategy%20involves%20renovating%20a%20property%2C%20renting%20it%20out%2C%20and%20then%20refinancing%20to%20pull%20out%20capital%20%E2%80%94%20ideally%20recouping%20most%20or%20all%20of%20the%20initial%20investment%20while%20retaining%20ownership%20of%20the%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20isn't%20risk-free.%20You%20still%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20numbers%20work%20and%20you%20can%20hit%20the%20value%20you're%20expecting%2C%20Hart%20pointed%20out%3A%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20get-go%2C%20you%20still%20have%20the%20risk%20of%20rehab%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20running%20correct%20costs%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20can%20actually%20get%20a%20good%20appraisal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20compared%20to%20flipping%2C%20BRRRR%20offers%20a%20more%20predictable%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20taking%20out%20the%20risk%20of%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Hart.%20Instead%20of%20worrying%20about%20a%20flip%20sitting%20for%20months%20while%20you're%20paying%20interest%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20know%20that%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20rehab%20you%20can%20get%20a%20tenant%20in%20there%20and%20you%20can%20immediately%20refinance%20with%20the%20bank.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20not%20result%20in%20quick%20cash%20like%20a%20successful%20flip%20can%2C%20but%20they're%20playing%20the%20long%20game%20anyways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20a%20BRRRR%20doesn't%20pencil%20out%20perfectly%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20holding%20onto%20the%20asset%20can%20still%20pay%20off%20over%20time%2C%20said%20Gorius%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20is%2C%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20time%20does%20heal%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20to%20bring%20%2410%2C000%20to%20the%20table%20to%20refinance%20and%20pay%20off%20a%20private%20lender%2C%20at%20least%20you%20still%20own%20the%20asset%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20put%20tenants%20in%20there%2C%20and%20maybe%20you%20lose%20%24100%20a%20month%20at%20first%20%E2%80%94%20not%20saying%20Kevin%20and%20I%20do%20this%20%E2%80%94%20but%20over%20time%2C%20rent%20will%20go%20up%20and%20eventually%2C%20you'll%20get%20that%20%2410%2C000%20back.%20Eventually%2C%20you%20won't%20lose%20%24100%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20you'll%20make%20%24100.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-strategy-home-flipping-brrrr-method-financing-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1767695401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F695c196c832e0ef1ead72e10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-strategy-home-flipping-brrrr-method-financing-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Find%20out%20why%20Louisville%20real%20estate%20investors%20Mike%20Gorius%20and%20Kevin%20Hart%20are%20moving%20from%20flipping%20in%202026%20and%20leaning%20into%20the%20BRRRR%20method.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-strategy-home-flippi