-chat-logs-train-models-safety-privacy-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edraft%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20aimed%20at%20governing%20%26quot%3Bhuman-like%26quot%3B%20interactive%20AI%20services%2C%20including%20chatbots%20and%20virtual%20companions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Cyberspace%20Administration%20of%20China%20said%20Beijing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-integrate-ai-consolidation-us-openai-paywall-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eencourages%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%26quot%3Bhuman-like%26quot%3B%20AI%2C%20but%20will%20put%20guardrails%20in%20place%20to%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20abuse%20and%20loss%20of%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWei%20Sun%2C%20the%20principal%20analyst%20for%20AI%20at%20Counterpoint%20Research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20draft%20measures%20send%20a%20signal%20that%20Beijing%20wants%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20development%20of%20human-like%20AI%20interactions%2C%20while%20keeping%20them%20regulated%20and%20socially%20acceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20AI%20industry%20has%20continued%20to%20move%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace%20since%20the%20start%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20DeepSeek%2C%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20most%20closely%20watched%20AI%20startups%2C%20published%20research%20outlining%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-new-ai-training-models-scale-manifold-constrained-analysts-china-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20training%20approach%20%3C%2Fa%3Eintended%20to%20make%20large%20models%20easier%20to%20scale.%20Analysts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20technique%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BManifold-Constrained%20Hyper-Connections%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20mHC%2C%20stood%20out%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbreakthrough%26quot%3B%20in%20model%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post%20reported%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20DeepSeek%20has%20updated%20the%20int